OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with rain spreading
OL,7,Ffrom the west, turning heavy across
OL,8,Fthe northwest. Drier around Nairn.
OL,9,FWindy with strong to gale
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FHeavy rain clearing away
OL,13,Fthrough the morning followed by bright
OL,14,Fspells and showers. Snow on hills.
OL,15,FStrong southwesterly winds, gales
OL,16,Falong the west coast later.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold
OL,19,Fwith bright spells and wintry showers
OL,20,Fon Friday and Saturday, Further rain
OL,21,Ffollowed by showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
